author: David Moye
title: Russian Women Compete To Be Bitten By Mosquitoes
text:
Russian Women Compete To Be Bitten By Mosquitoes Newser.com 
Mosquitoe are the scourge of every corner of the Earth except for Berezniki, Russia. 
That's where the Russian Mosquito Festival begins on Friday. 
The big event is the "Most Delicious Girl" contest in which women compete to see who can attract the most mosquito bites in 20 minutes.
